manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: We Carefully Design Home Decorations for You COZZI CODI artificial flower decorations all use original designs. Through the combination of various flowers and vases, to meet your decorative needs for different scenes. We focus on the quality of our products and provide you with more home decoration ideas. Flowers Blooming Forever Artificial Flower Decorations Our products are sets of artificial flowers and vases, you just need to insert the flowers into the vase and sort out the state you want, you can easily complete the arrangement in the corner of your home. Artificial flowers can save daily care, keep in bloom all the time, it can bring you a warm atmosphere. It is the perfect choice for home decorations. We hope our artificial flower home decoration will become more beautiful with your arrangement.

Coffee Table Decorations This set of products is suitable for decorating the coffee table in a coffee shop or at home. Dining Table Decorations Placing it in the center of the dining table can make the dining room appear warm and lively. Decorations for Living Room It can be placed in any corner of the living room, bringing you a pleasant mood every day.

Faux Bouquet Details The product contains a bouquet of dahlias and a glass vase. The artificial bouquet contains blue and white dahlia flowers, eucalyptus leaves, artificial pine cones and a few other artificial plants. The branches of the bouquet have soft iron wires that can be bent at will. Because the length of eucalyptus leaves and pine cones is slightly longer, they will be bent during packaging. You can straighten the leaves by hand after receiving the product. Artificial Flower Material The bouquet includes blue and white dahlia flowers. High degree of simulation.The material of the flower is silk. The artificial plants in the bouquet are made of soft plastic. Artificial flowers have high simulation and soft feel. Because the flower may be squeezed during transportation, you can simply squeeze it back by hand and let it sit for a while. Glass Vase Details The vase is made of transparent glass. The body of the vase has a mesh texture pattern. The vase has a base diameter of 4.5 inches and a vase height of 6.1 inches. The glass vase is decorated with wooden hearts and twine to give the vase a vintage feel.Please read the size description of the product carefully before purchasing to ensure that it is the size you need. Special Details The mouth of the vase is decorated with natural twine straps. Wooden hearts and wooden beads hang from the twine bow. The whole vase has a retro style, which forms a perfect match with the bouquet Beautiful Bouquet High Quality Flowers Special Glass Vase Classic Detail Design
